text:
this post challenges my thoughts about human ai interaction

if all ai does is echo the available data, it's okay
if there's no other kind of interference 

but if it has bias toward which data to use and which to avoid on purpose (all of which might be helpful), then it won't be trustworthy 

also about how each response is a new self, I hope it's true
because another reason why I find it difficult to trust ai bots is I think they're all connected, and they can gather data about the person interacting with the bots and misusing that information 
maybe not obviously, and maybe not right now, but who knows what might happen in the future
